The paper discusses active learning methods for outlier detection with one-class classifiers, which involves machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these fields are also relevant to the topic of active learning and outlier detection.
